380
00:29:14,029 --> 00:29:15,699
- Yes.
- Can we go together?

381
00:29:15,699 --> 00:29:17,830
Okay, let's go.

382
00:29:21,210 --> 00:29:22,879
Are they your friends?

383
00:29:22,879 --> 00:29:24,919
