426
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,440
Taotao!

427
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:38,180
Taotao.

428
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:40,689
- What's wrong, Taotao?
- Le Tao, are you okay?

429
00:31:40,689 --> 00:31:42,750
I'm fine.

430
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:45,700
