433
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:57,629
- Don't cry, Le Tao.
- Taotao.

434
00:31:57,629 --> 00:31:59,619
- Don't cry, Taotao.
- Taotao.

435
00:31:59,619 --> 00:32:01,369
